            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/advisor/tools/budget">ðŸ’° Budget Calculator</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item active" href="/advisor/tools/goal">ðŸŽ¯ Goal Savings Calculator</a></li>
